snippet.title: The Hunter: Primal Review (early access) - Worth a buy
snippet.description:
The Hunter Primal review is it worth a buy?

Hunt - Explore - Survive The most realistic prehistoric survival game ever created. Featuring a huge Jurassic environment populated by horrifying all-stars such as T-Rex, Triceratops, Utahraptor. The hunting & wildlife experience of the renowned developer Expansive Worlds is combined with all new survival elements
